hivien.net/Ung-%C4%90%C3%A0o/author-54CdLotgLgjZolehyx7oYw">Ung Đào</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%C3%B3ng-thuy%E1%BB%81n-T%E1%BB%91ng-kh%C3%A1ch-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%C3%AA-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-NEB-pU40M9FIVCdT1DUKtg">Phóng thuyền (Tống khách Thương Khê huyện) - 放船（送客蒼溪縣）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Tr%E1%BB%9F-binh-h%C3%A0nh/poem-wLBO_S7oDu5BwDnRbL0Axg">Trở binh hành - 阻兵行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%B3-b%C3%A0-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Tỳ bà hành - 琵琶行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C5%A9-trung-qu%C3%A1-Th%E1%BA%A5t-L%C3%BD-lung-ca/poem-t1zljGkZZw_rj7vXYCTTVw">Vũ trung quá Thất Lý lung ca - 雨中過七里瀧歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/author-leXS2a46kBYHa9AoDh5zfw">Ngô Tích Kỳ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
